detail.010_HL.150_REF.definition:
A total of three REF segments may be used within this loop, as defined below. The Bill
of Lading Number is mandatory. A Carrier Reference Number (PRO/Invoice) and an
additional tracking number may also be provided optionally.

detail.010_HL.220_N1.220_N1.definition: - the code 92 in N103 represents the CVS store number
